{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":7,"day":1}],"page_start":4,"page_end":4,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"红军不怕远征难——为红军长征三十年而作","authors":["萧华/毛泽东/董辰生"],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征是历史纪录上的第一次，长征是宣言书，长征是宣传队，长征是播种机。……长征是以我们胜利、敌人失败的结果而告结束。  毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军号响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"子弟兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别故乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军主力上征途，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战略转移去远方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女老少来相送，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热泪沾衣叙情长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌云遮天难持久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红日永远放光芒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命一定要胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人终于被埋葬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、突破封锁线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路迢迢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌重重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军情忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军夜渡于都河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"固陂新田打胜仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佯攻汝城占宜章，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨过潇水抢湘江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十昼夜飞行军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突破四道封锁墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"围追堵截奈我何，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数十万敌空惆怅！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、进遵义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苗岭秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"溪水清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百鸟啼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报新春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌江天险挡不住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娄山刀坝歼敌兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遵义会议放光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全党全军齐欢庆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众欢呼毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农踊跃当红军。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英明领袖来掌舵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命磅礴向前进。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、入云南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横断山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路难行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌重兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压黔境。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士双脚走天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声东击西出奇兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌江天险重飞渡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兵临贵阳逼昆明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人弃甲丢烟枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我军乘胜赶路程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"调虎离山袭金沙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席用兵妙如神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五、飞越大渡河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水湍急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山峭耸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄关险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豺狼凶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"健儿巧渡金沙江，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟民族夹道迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安顺场畔孤舟勇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩波踏浪歼敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昼夜兼程二百四，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猛打猛追夺泸定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁索桥上威风显，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勇士万代留英名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六、过雪山草地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪皑皑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野茫茫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高原寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炊断粮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军都是钢铁汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千锤百炼不怕难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山低头迎远客，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草毯泥毡扎营盘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨侵衣骨更硬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野菜充饥志愈坚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官兵一致同甘苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命理想高于天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七、到吴起镇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锣鼓响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秧歌起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长城喜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腊子口上神兵降，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百丈悬崖当云梯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六盘山上红旗展，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"势如破竹扫敌骑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陕甘军民传喜讯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"征师胜利到吴起。〔注一〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南北兄弟手携手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扩大前进根据地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八、祝捷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大雪飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗征尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌进攻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送礼品。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长途跋涉足未稳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌军围攻形势紧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"主席战场来指挥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全军振奋杀敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直罗满山炮声急，〔注二〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万余敌兵一网尽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"活捉敌酋牛师长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民凯歌高入云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九、报喜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手足情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传佳音。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英勇二、四方面军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转战数省久闻名。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历尽千辛万般苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利会聚甘孜城。〔注三〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏破岷山千里雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高歌北进并肩行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边区军民喜若狂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗招展迎亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十、大会师"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军号响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战马吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流两万五千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军威名天下扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三支劲旅大会师，〔注四〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日寇胆破蒋魂丧。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军也乐来民也乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万水千山齐歌唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱领袖毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌唱伟大共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十一、会师献礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志凌云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山城堡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军威振。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜色朦胧群山隐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三军奋勇杀敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光万道迎空舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霹雳一声动地鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟并肩显身手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛歼蒋贼王牌军。〔注五〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旭日东升照战场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会师献礼载功勋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二、誓师抗日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日寇侵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灾难深。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当逃兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红军集结陕甘宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抗日风暴卷烟云。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼吁停战驱日寇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我党宣言普天应。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"军民怒火千万丈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥戈誓师大进军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排山倒海风雷起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放祖国大地春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六五年五月"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注解："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔一〕中央红军一九三四年十月中旬开始长征，于一九三五年十月二十一日到达陕北根据地吴起镇（今吴旗县），与陕北红军和自鄂豫皖根据地长征先行到达陕北的红二十五军胜利会师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔二〕指陕西省邸县直罗镇战役。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔三〕红军第二方面军于一九三五年十一月开始长征，一九三六年六月与正在长征途中的红四方面军在原西康省甘孜地区（今属四川省）会合。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔四〕红军二、四方面军和中央红军于一九三六年十月在甘肃省会宁地区会师。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔五〕红军三大主力会师后，在陕北山城堡地区，全歼蒋介石的精锐胡宗南一个师。这是第二次国内革命战争时期的最后一仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上图：告别"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右上图：大会师  董辰生插图"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}